Package main.java.entities

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Archive
    Archive is the class that contains most, if not all, of the methods related to serialization and data storage.
    Employee
    Employee is a subClass of User that has restricted permissions.
    Manager
    Employee is a subClass of User that has more permissions.
    Shell
    Shell class serves as a barrier that encapsulates the application's specific classes, entities and methods.
    Task
    Task represents, as the name indicates, a specific task with an identifiable name, author and assignee.
    User
    User is an abstract class that defines methods and attributes common to both manager and employee types.
